name: NFT Stalker Mag #3: MekaVerse
description:
8,888 unique Mekas who need Drivers. The MekaVerse is a collection of 8,888 generative Mekas with hundreds of elements inspired by the Japan Mecha universes.

Each artwork is original, with its own color palette and creation. The objective was to make each Meka unique in order to prioritize quality above quantity.
